_sText:
![Introduction](https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/17061503/gb/introduction.png "Introduction")

I noticed a distinct lack of dark DM based maps for CS:S (which nobody plays anymore, right?), so I set out and produced this, a long time ago, [6 months in fact.](http://gamebanana.com/wips/42554 "")

I may consider converting this to CS:Go should there be enough of an attraction, though I personally do not think it's up to the quality of which CS:Go demands, specifically, more detail to the exterior areas.

![Features](https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/17061503/gb/features.png "Features")

- 3 level "Ware" / "Power" house, plus an accessible roof
- Dark low lighting levels throughout
- Good optimization for AI / offline play
- Balanced, various connectors / drop downs.
